      "text": "• 节点 (Node) - 位置 xyz\n• TrailEdge - 顺序边\n  - length > 0: 拉力\n  - length < 0: 压力\n• DeviationEdge - 偏移边\n  - force: 目标力\n• Supports - 支撑节点\n• Loads - 荷载",
