      "fontFamily": 2,
      "text": "# 1. 创建拓扑图\n topology = TopologyDiagram()\n topology.add_node(Node(0, [0.0, 0.0, 0.0]))\n topology.add_edge(TrailEdge(0, 1, length=-1.5))  # 压力\n topology.add_support(NodeSupport(0))\n topology.add_load(NodeLoad(1, [0.0, -1.0, 0.0]))\n\n # 2. 构建 Trails\n topology.build_trails()\n\n # 3. 计算平衡\n form = static_equilibrium(topology, eta=1e-6, tmax=100)\n\n # 4. 可视化\n viewer = Viewer()\n viewer.scene.add(topology)\n viewer.scene.add(form)\n viewer.show()",
